JOSEPH De VITO, PETITIONER-RESPONDENT, v. MULLEN’S ROOFING COMPANY, RESPONDENT-PETITIONER. Messrs. Shaw, Pindar, McElroy, Connell & Foley for the petitioner. Messrs. David & Albert L. Cohn and Mr. Richard Lifland for the respondent. April 30, 1962.

See same case below: 72 N. J. Super. 233.
